    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "OLYMPIC\nWINTER SCHEDULES\nUNITED STATES CANADA\nEUROPE • MIDDLE EAST\nAFRICA\nNOVEMBER 1, 1969 — MARCH 31, 1970",
      "Amsteroam\nLondon\nFrankfurt\nZurich\nnessa oniki\nRome\nMontreal\nAthens\nChicago\n• Istanbul\nNicosia\n• Beirut\nTel Aviv\nNew York\nCairo\nOlympic\nhas important\nconnections.\nWe fly to 20 of the most\nimportant cities in the United\nStates, Canada, Europe, the\nMiddle East and Africa. And\nnobody has better\nconnections throughout\nGreece and its Golden Isles.\nWherever you're going, you\ncan enjoy our celebrated\nfoods and wines and superb\nservice on the way.\nOLYMPIC\nNairobi\nJohannesburg."
    ],
